description: Home of the Original Chicago Style Hotdog, Italian Beef Sandwich, Smoked All Beef Sausage and Good Humor Ice Cream We use the best food products from Vienna Beef Welcome to the original Chicago Style Hotdog Joint where we build the best Chicago Style Hotdogs and Italian Beef Sandwiches you’ve ever had. We start with only the freshest products from Vienna Beef and build it just the way they do in Chicago. We are locally owned and operated. We are known for our famous Vienna Beef Chicago Style Hotdogs and Italian Beef Sandwiches. Our story is simple, we started with a hotdog cart vending on street corners in 2005, then we opened a Food Truck and we have grown into one of Florida's Premier Mobile Food Event Companies. With our new custom food truck your event diners can expect a variety of food with quick service. We are licensed by the state of Florida, fully insured and ready to set up at your next event! We now serve Good Humor Ice Cream on the truck!!
name: Joey's Chicago Style Food
